<a id="dingsx36884" href="javascript:dingsx('36884','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=a81fa690a161')">有用(0)</a><a id="paisx36884" style=" margin-left:10px;" href="javascript:paisx('36884','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=a81fa690a161')">没用(1)</a>
